      <sentence>
        <infon key="n">10</infon>
        <offset>1360</offset>
        <text>The two methods showed major differences in cell volume and cell C frequency distributions.
</text>
      </sentence>
      <sentence>
        <infon key="n">11</infon>
        <offset>1452</offset>
        <text>This study refines the methodology for quantifying bacteria-mediated C fluxes and the role of bacteria in marine ecosystems, and suggests the potential of AFM for individual cell physiological interrogations in natural marine assemblages.
</text>
